===Noun===
'''jiffy''' ([[jiffies]])

# (''colloquial'') A very short non-specific period of time.
#:''I'll be back in a jiffy.''
# (''computers'') A unit of time defined by its basic timer's frequency; historically and by convention this is 1/100th of a second, but this can vary in alternative or newer versions of operating systems.